Usage:
| Script | Command |
| --- | --- |
| TempPrefetchCleaner.py | `python TempPrefetchCleaner.py` |
| DirectorySizeReport.py | `python DirectorySizeReport.py --path . --top 10` |
| TopLargestFiles.py | `python TopLargestFiles.py --path . --top 20` |
| FileExtensionCounter.py | `python FileExtensionCounter.py --path .` |
| MoveFilesByExtension.py | `python MoveFilesByExtension.py --path .` |
| RenameExtensions.py | `python RenameExtensions.py --path . --old .txt --new .md` |
| RemoveEmptyDirs.py | `python RemoveEmptyDirs.py --path .` |
| ArchiveFolderToZip.py | `python ArchiveFolderToZip.py --source . --dest archive.zip` |
| ExtractZipHere.py | `python ExtractZipHere.py --zip archive.zip --dest .` |
| BackupDirectory.py | `python BackupDirectory.py --source . --dest backups` |
| SyncDirectories.py | `python SyncDirectories.py --source . --dest backup --dry-run` |
| OldFilesCleaner.py | `python OldFilesCleaner.py --path . --days 30` |
| DuplicateFileFinder.py | `python DuplicateFileFinder.py --path .` |
| HashFile.py | `python HashFile.py --path file.txt --algo sha256` |
| VerifyFileHash.py | `python VerifyFileHash.py --path file.txt --expected <hash>` |
| GeneratePassword.py | `python GeneratePassword.py --length 16 --count 3` |
| Base64EncodeFile.py | `python Base64EncodeFile.py --input file.bin --output file.b64` |
| Base64DecodeFile.py | `python Base64DecodeFile.py --input file.b64 --output file.bin` |
